OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing on and off this evening,
OL,7,Flargely easing as skies clear during
OL,8,Fthe second half of the night.
OL,9,FGenerally breezy, with locally gusty
OL,10,Fwinds developing, particularly over
OL,11,Fthe higher Pennine routes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FVariable amounts of cloud but
OL,14,Fa dry, fairly bright and breezy day
OL,15,Ffor many. Some intermittent rain
OL,16,Fpossible at times, mainly across
OL,17,Fwestern hills. Feeling warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
