OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain giving way to sunshine and
OL,7,Fshowers on Monday. Temperatures
OL,8,Ftrending lower. Rather cool and breezy
OL,9,FTuesday and Wednesday with sunny
OL,10,Fspells, scattered showers and possible
OL,11,Fafternoon thunderstorms.
